name: Kiki Psycho | Kiki's Playground #14
description: What is Kiki's Playground?  It's an artist collective that is available for new and experienced artists to find inspiration and have a fun social platform to work with!  Create what inspires you when you think about Kiki, and Kiki will take care of the minting fees!  The cut is 90/10 with the artist retaining the majority split, always.  Artist: RealSmokingGod
